"Rare Pair in the Greenscape":
"I've just received word of two rare species sightings.
They're calling them a Banse Ang and Banse Dona--a
pair of gigantic native species that can be found racing
across the Greenscape of Naberius. Despite the
eyewitness reports we've received, we know so little
about them that they're still shrouded in mystery. That's
why I would like you to go investigate at once. I'll await
your hopefully favorable response.
*Target: Banse Angs and
Banse Donas level 41 or higher"

"希少種の目撃情報が寄せられた。
バンサ・オングとバンサ・ドンナ。
惑星ナベリウスの森林を一対で疾走する
巨大な原生種だ。
目撃報告はあるものの、実情はまだまだ
謎に包まれ、未解明な部分が多い。
だからこそ、早く調査を行いたいのだ。
良い返事を期待しているよ。
※Lv.41以上のバンサ・オング
バンサ・ドンナが対象"
